com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface Geometry

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    LinearRing, LineString, Point, Polygon

    public interface Geometry
    This interface represents the <Geometry> abstract tag from KML specification. It provides a placeholder object for all derived Geometry objects.
